As a native Japanese, I wish that they made authentic sushi for the level three. What Level three chef made is American sushi. Neither spicy tuna nor avocado is traditionally Japanese filling and that's just a few of the many differences.

I do enjoy American sushi, but I would have loved to see the traditional art of sushi featured in this series.
